    "title": "California wants to hear from you — on AI, jobs, and what comes next",
    "excerpt": "<p>California has a question for you. What are your thoughts on AI? You have a way to tell California’s leaders in government how you feel, right now. Your responses will be used to help shape what the state does next. This is not just another comment box that disappears into the void. This is a &#8230; <a title=\"California wants to hear from you — on AI, jobs, and what comes next\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/2026/05/26/california-wants-to-hear-from-you-on-ai-jobs-and-what-comes-next/\" aria-label=\"More on California wants to hear from you — on AI, jobs, and what comes next\">Read more</a></p>\n",
